
### Admin Dashboard & Refinements
- **Admin Dashboard**: Created a dedicated dashboard for tracking AI investment and usage.
  - **Route**: `/dashboard/admin`
  - **Features**:
    - **Total Investment**: Real-time tracking of total AI costs in BDT (à§³).
    - **Cost Breakdown**: Visual charts (Pie & Bar) separating costs by feature (Image Recognition, Chatbot, Auto-tagging).
    - **Usage History**: 30-day timeline of AI spending.
  - **Currency**: Converted all costs to BDT (approx. 1 USD = 120 BDT).
- **Dashboard Overview**:
  - Removed "AI Cost" card from the main user dashboard to keep it focused on business metrics (Orders, Revenue, Messages).
  - Updated layout to a clean 3-column grid.
- **Files Created/Modified**:
  - `app/dashboard/admin/page.tsx` (New)
  - `app/api/admin/usage/route.ts` (New)
  - `app/dashboard/page.tsx` (Modified)
